NOC-Kit news
============

CHANGES IN NOC-KIT VERSION 0.1.0:

  NEW FEATURES:

    * showsigs.c: new tool
    
    * slaughter.sh: new tool (and alias slaughterall.sh)

  IMPROVEMENTS:

    * None

  CHANGES IN BEHAVIOUR:

    * N/A

  BUG FIXES:

    * N/A

  TODO (PLANNED):

    * Manpages/Info pages

    * better --help output

CHANGES IN NOC-KIT VERSION 0.2.0:

  NEW FEATURES:

    * zfd.sh: new tool

    * nk_utils.sh (__scriptname, __scriptbasename, __scriptdirname,
                   __usage_footer, __version, __usage, __info, __warn, __die,
                   __filter, __reduce, __list_create, __list_destroy,
                   __list_append, __list_prepend, __list_insert, __list_pop,
                   __list_shift, __list_splice, __list_length, __list_iterate,
                   __list_slice, __list_reverse, __list_sort, __lambda,
                   __map): new source functions


    * nk_tests.sh (__on, __off, __ison, __isoff, __eql, __neq, __has, __empty,
                   __notempty): new source functions

  IMPROVEMENTS:

    * Split and improved shell libs

  CHANGES IN BEHAVIOUR:

    * New syntax for all internal functions and vars

  BUG FIXES:

    * N/A

  TODO (PLANNED):

    * Manpages/Info pages

    * better --help output
